; Copy to userlist.txt (gitignored) only if you switch the edoburu image to a
; mounted auth_file. By default the image derives credentials from the
; DB_USER/DB_PASSWORD env vars in docker-compose.yml, so no userlist is needed.
"authenticator" "md5<hash-of-password-plus-username>"
"postgres" "md5<hash-of-password-plus-username>"
